Given	I'm logged-in with valid credentials
And I select 'Yes' radio button from 'Contrast enhanced' in Page 03
And	I go to Page 04 of Thoracic MRI

When I select 'Finding' radio button
Then 'Finding' dropdown menu is enabled

When I select 'Cardiovascular/Heart' from the dropdown menu
Then 'Right' checkbox is enabled
And 'Left' checkbox is enabled
And 'Pericardium' checkbox is enabled

When I select 'Right' checkbox
Then 'Atrial enlargement' checkbox is enabled
And 'Ventricle enlargement' checkbox is enabled
And 'Thickening of myocardium' checkbox is enabled
And 'Venous contrast medium reflux' checkbox is enabled
And 'Thrombus' checkbox is enabled

When I select 'Left' checkbox
Then 'Atrial enlargement' checkbox is enabled
And 'Ventricle enlargement' checkbox is enabled
And 'Thickening of myocardium' checkbox is enabled
And 'Thrombus' checkbox is enabled

When I select 'Pericardium' checkbox
Then 'Effusion' checkbox is enabled
And 'Mass' checkbox is enabled
And 'Pneumopericardium' checkbox is enabled
And 'Focal signal void' checkbox is enabled

When I select 'Effusion' checkbox
Then 'Max. width in mm' input field is enabled
When I select 'Mass' checkbox
Then 'Max. diameter in mm' input field is enabled
When I select 'Focal signal void' checkbox
Then 'Calcification' radio button is enabled
And 'Air' radio button is enabled
And 'Fibrosis' radio button is enabled
And 'Pericarditis constrictiva' checkbox is enabled